HEADWORD: Xe
<hw>Xe</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The chemical symbol for the
chemical element <er>xenon</er>, having atomic number 54; it is one of
the six noble gases.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> xenon.</syn>⟦br⟧
